{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Gladio Mori is a physics-driven fighting game that redefines the gladiator arena. Whether playing solo or challenging others in multiplayer battles, you\u2019ll wield razor-sharp weapons and unleash unique moves in brutal, tactical combat. Every decision, swing, and step matters as you carve your path to victory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2689120/extras/GM_Basic_V2.gif?t=1733214739\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Multiplayer</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Take on opponents in intense online battles with up to 4 players or enjoy the action locally with split-screen gameplay. Prove your skill and adaptability in every fight as you rise to claim victory in the arena.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2689120/extras/Separator-GM.png?t=1733214739\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Organ-Based Damage System</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Forget health bars\u2014combat in Gladio Mori is as brutal as it is precise. Damage to muscles, arteries, and vitals directly impacts your ability to fight:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Injured Muscles</strong> weaken your strikes.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Severed Arteries</strong> cause you to bleed out.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Pierced Vitals</strong> mean instant death.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Precision and strategy are your greatest weapons.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2689120/extras/GM_DamageSystem_V2.gif?t=1733214739\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Authentic Weapons and Armor</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">No magical gear here\u2014just realistic weapons and armor that behave as they should. Plate armor blocks strikes, but exposes weak points. Find openings in your opponent\u2019s defenses or risk being outmatched.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2689120/extras/GM_ArmourSystem_V2.gif?t=1733214739\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>In-Game Move Editor</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unleash your creativity with a fully customizable move editor. Control your character\u2019s physical body to craft unique animations:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Design efficient and devastating attacks.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Recreate iconic moves from your favorite films or games.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Experiment with wild, unpredictable maneuvers\u2014it's up to you.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2689120/extras/GM_MoveEditor_V2.gif?t=1733214739\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Community-Created Moves</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Not an animator? No problem. Explore movesets shared by other players or mix and match individual moves to create a style that\u2019s entirely yours. The community fuels the creativity in Gladio Mori.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2689120/extras/GM_Community_V2.gif?t=1733214739\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Enter the Arena</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Every battle in Gladio Mori is a test of strategy, skill, and ingenuity. Forge your fighting style, exploit weaknesses, and prove your worth in the ultimate arena.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The gladiator's path awaits\u2014are you ready?</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2689120/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1733214739","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2689120/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1733214739","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2689120/3e9d4322fe6e4fd30494a0e141d891e6e5c3cb2f/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1733214739","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2689120/3e9d4322fe6e4fd30494a0e141d891e6e5c3cb2f/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1733214739","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"PvP","id":49},{"description":"Online PvP","id":36},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen PvP","id":37},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen","id":24},{"description":"Partial Controller Support","id":18},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[5],"notes":"The game is fairly stylized, but it does include unrealistic but frequent violence."},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Gladio Mori is a physics-driven fighting game that redefines the gladiator arena. Whether playing solo or challenging others in multiplayer battles, you\u2019ll wield razor-sharp weapons and unleash unique moves in brutal, tactical combat. Every decision, swing, and step matters as you carve your path to victory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2689120/extras/GM_Basic_V2.gif?t=1733214739\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Multiplayer</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Take on opponents in intense online battles with up to 4 players or enjoy the action locally with split-screen gameplay. Prove your skill and adaptability in every fight as you rise to claim victory in the arena.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2689120/extras/Separator-GM.png?t=1733214739\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Organ-Based Damage System</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Forget health bars\u2014combat in Gladio Mori is as brutal as it is precise. Damage to muscles, arteries, and vitals directly impacts your ability to fight:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Injured Muscles</strong> weaken your strikes.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Severed Arteries</strong> cause you to bleed out.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Pierced Vitals</strong> mean instant death.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Precision and strategy are your greatest weapons.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2689120/extras/GM_DamageSystem_V2.gif?t=1733214739\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Authentic Weapons and Armor</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">No magical gear here\u2014just realistic weapons and armor that behave as they should. Plate armor blocks strikes, but exposes weak points. Find openings in your opponent\u2019s defenses or risk being outmatched.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2689120/extras/GM_ArmourSystem_V2.gif?t=1733214739\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>In-Game Move Editor</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unleash your creativity with a fully customizable move editor. Control your character\u2019s physical body to craft unique animations:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Design efficient and devastating attacks.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Recreate iconic moves from your favorite films or games.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Experiment with wild, unpredictable maneuvers\u2014it's up to you.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2689120/extras/GM_MoveEditor_V2.gif?t=1733214739\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Community-Created Moves</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Not an animator? No problem. Explore movesets shared by other players or mix and match individual moves to create a style that\u2019s entirely yours. The community fuels the creativity in Gladio Mori.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2689120/extras/GM_Community_V2.gif?t=1733214739\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Enter the Arena</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Every battle in Gladio Mori is a test of strategy, skill, and ingenuity. Forge your fighting style, exploit weaknesses, and prove your worth in the ultimate arena.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The gladiator's path awaits\u2014are you ready?</p>","developers":["Plebeian Studio"],"genres":[{"description":"Action","id":"1"},{"description":"Simulation","id":"28"},{"description":"Early Access","id":"70"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2689120/header.jpg?t=1733214739","is_free":false,"linux_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"},"mac_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul